title My personal site archive
date 2012-02-21

paragraph
 I found it mildly interesting to dig up my old homepages and put them in this git.
 This folder contains some old sites from before 2010. This would not have been possible without the Internet Archive's Wayback Machine ❤️.

title3 August 2007

paragraph
 It looks like I registered breckyunits.com on August 24th, 2007. It appears I used Wordpress to first host my blog. Here's <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20070907182730/http://www.breckyunits.com/">what it looked like that September</a>. There's a Flash widget on there. The title of the site is "The Best Blog on the Internet". I think it was a good joke. I had just recently graduated college, and had not yet moved to the West Coast.

