title3 December 2009

paragraph
 In December 2009 I wrote my own blog software called <a href="https://github.com/breck7/brecksblog">brecksblog</a> and here's what my new site <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20091204020806/http://breckyunits.com/">looked like</a>. I kept it simple, and that paid dividends as my <a href="https://breckyunits.com/">current homepage</a>, now powered by Scroll, evolved from that.
 
